{"tid":516440,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港要發展就要起賭場","createTime":"2018-01-01T12:02:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T14:12:21.000Z","uid":146595,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ac16e862785857d7dd0b0aa5296d384a2524ba08","tid":516440,"uid":146595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:02:25.000Z","msg":"香港呢d已發展地區本身傳統行業好多營利已經停濟不前<br />\n要特破就一定要有新元素<br />\n如果可以開賭場連澳門既生意都搶埋<br />\n除左可以增加就業 重帶動到好多周邊經濟<br />\n<br />\n不過實有道德撚話賭博唔好乜乜乜 <br />\n但係本身香港已經有馬會做緊賭博事業（仲要係攏斷市場）<br />\n所以唔覺得開多間賭場會造成咩問題"},{"pid":"e7340f3d390b9a979c4e023631b59e3b25ce5031","tid":516440,"uid":2126,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:10:38.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"2eff938f58c8008ba6ffa525ff0dacaec772d674","tid":516440,"uid":154756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:19:01.000Z","msg":"388 咪係賭場"},{"pid":"d2e2c7f1b3787d2e10c50c4fd33e5e1639d3b64d","tid":516440,"uid":29675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:22:43.000Z","msg":"香港賭場=股市<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3388d33f789140978be3c3ab94745bc0513bca32","tid":516440,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:29:35.000Z","msg":"紅燈區"},{"pid":"17030bbe80acf336e3d8a66082e22d53760c928b","tid":516440,"uid":108266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:37:57.000Z","msg":"股市咪賭場"},{"pid":"d1657b726a045802dceb6d5e7021d65f9aa3f347","tid":516440,"uid":146595,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e7340f3d390b9a979c4e023631b59e3b25ce5031","tid":516440,"uid":2126,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T12:10:38.000Z","msg":"On9"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T13:55:12.000Z","msg":"On9連登仔 唔支持就講個理據出黎 講句on9就當駁左？"},{"pid":"3bf0213a58ec9becb68f665926a6193a816e8447","tid":516440,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d1657b726a045802dceb6d5e7021d65f9